title: You Have Been Programmed
itunes:title: You Have Been Programmed
description:
If someone cusses, does it offend you? If so, have you ever asked yourself why? See, since the moment we come into this world we are programmed. It's not a bad thing, it's just the way the world is. In this episode, I want to talk about your programming and teach you how to unravel all your programmings.
